{
  "name": "Rally the Troops",
  "type": "feat",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 18th level, you are the bastion that holds the line. When you use your Action Surge feature, select a number of creatures equal to half of your Charisma modifier (rounded down) within 60 feet of you that can see and hear you. They can use their reaction to immediately take an additional action as if it were their turn. As part of that action, they can't make more than 2 weapon attacks, and any spells cast must be of 5th level or lower.</p>",
